high_descs: Turn right and take eleven steps, turn right again to face the counter.
Pick up the large knife with the yellow handle.
Turn right and walk straight to the counter, turn left and stop.
Slice the tomato by the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the knife behind the egg with the blade pointing left.
Put a slice of tomato in the microwave in front of the knife’s handle, standing up.
Shut the door and turn on the microwave for a few seconds, open the door and take out only the tomato and shut the door.
Turn left for five steps, turn left for one step and stop to face the table.
Put the tomato slice on the table in front of the salt shaker, standing vertically with the face to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato on the table, standing up.

high_descs: Turn right and face the island to your right.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave behind you.
Slice the tomato on the right of the microwave in front of you.
Open the microwave in front of you and place the knife inside.
Take a tomato slice and place the slice in the microwave in front of you.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave in front of you and take it out.
Turn left and face the counter to your left.
Place the tomato slice on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice on the island.

high_descs: Turn right and stop at the kitchen island
Grab the large knife off of the counter
Turn left and go to the microwave
Cut the tomato on the right of the microwave into slices
Put the knife into the microwave
Grab a slice of tomato
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then take it out
Turn left and stop at the kitchen island
Put the tomato on the counter
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot sliced tomato on the kitchen island
